{"tid":1667994,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"各位 趁無咁多鬼推post 請聽我一言。","createTime":"2019-10-21T18:07:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T10:17:22.000Z","uid":114901,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bf575bf0d67ef174fe3f8ad25ccabed729c1276d","tid":1667994,"uid":114901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:08:00.000Z","msg":"真手足 唔會態度惡劣 <br />\n唔會開post狂屌 <br />\n唔會嘗試拉一派打一派<br />\n<br />\n好多標題一睇就知引戰味重，例如：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「今日你班前線點解釋xxx!」<br />\n「我屌曬你班xxx!」</span><br />\n<br />\n我覺得有人不斷尋找手足意識型態上嘅對立點<br />\n再加以放大<br />\n成功嘅post正負皮出現5:5,6:4比例，留言越鬧越勁<br />\n<br />\n有邊個敢講自己對策略上嘅睇法<br />\n一定係絕對真理？<br />\n不切不割 應該係大家嘅出發點同埋目的<br />\n當中既過程少不免有分歧<br />\n<br />\n如果你係真手足 但都試過大屌同路人<br />\n希望係下次網軍全面上場時 記住打醒精神<br />\n留言互相提醒應有嘅態度<br />\n<br />\n可檢討 不起鋼 多謝手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc1a3f9c5fd73761df17e771cd3c3a45818a396","tid":1667994,"uid":311563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T19:07:37.000Z","msg":"P牌輕輕一推<br />\n<br />\n其實呢啲好多人都知，不過都多謝樓主你開post講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e2a5ee5a7d07832f7b4736533f0a2b906796f02","tid":1667994,"uid":114901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T10:15:47.000Z","msg":"自推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"303e229062e0bc9e38074b2141d2d2dd0343807b","tid":1667994,"uid":311198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T10:17:22.000Z","msg":"Tui"}]}